OL,7,MRetro Radio Mic - Micron TX503         
OL,9,BI'm not much of a sound geek, but there
OL,10,Bis a distinctive looking radio mic that
OL,11,Bwas often seen on TV in the 80's, 90's 
OL,12,Band early 2000's that I'd always wanted
OL,13,Bto own - the Micron TX503. I finally   
OL,14,Bpicked one up from specialist TV       
OL,15,Bequipment auction site "Techbid" for   
OL,16,B#35, along with the matching receiver. 
OL,17,FThe mic needed little in the way of    
OL,18,Frestoration - I just dismantled it,    
OL,19,Fcleaned it up and applied a thin layer 
OL,20,Fof spray paint to the mic mesh as this 
OL,21,Fwas chipped.                           
OL,22,Q]MGvisit me onlineCretroworkshop.uk    
OL,24,ASinclair C5BSpectrum 48KCNewsFMainIndex
PN,40302
SC,0002
PS,C000
FL,401,402,404,101,8ff,400
OL,1,BThe receiver rack contains 8 receiver  
OL,2,Bmodules, and module no.8 had a damaged 
OL,3,Bhandle. I obtained a new part from     
OL,4,BDigikey, but this didnt fit correctly. 
OL,5,BWith a little modification using a     
OL,6,BDremmel and some fibre washers, it was 
OL,7,Btweaked into place.                    
OL,8,FA new engraved plate was prepared      
OL,9,Fby a local high street cobbler, and    
OL,10,Fthis was fixed to the module.          
OL,11,EI tested the microphone and found it to
OL,12,Ebe in fully working order. There is    
OL,13,Emore background noise than when using  
OL,14,Ea wired mic, but the fact that it      
OL,15,Ewas all working is testament to the    
OL,16,Eexcellent build quality.               
OL,17,AIn the video I take a look at audio    
OL,18,Acompanding, which is used by radiomics 
OL,19,Ato overcome the limited dynamic range  
OL,20,Ainherent in radio transmission.        
OL,21,CI also explain the radio channels used 
OL,22,Cfor radio mics, and discuss the        
OL,23,CUK licensing requirements.             
OL,24,ASinclair C5BSpectrum 48KCNewsFMainIndex
PN,40303
SC,0003
PS,C000
FL,401,402,404,101,8ff,400
OL,1,BThe mic will mainly be used as a       
OL,2,Bdisplay piece as it has unique design  
OL,3,Bappeal with its angular lines and      
OL,4,Bstainless steel finish. I think it is  
OL,5,Ba classic on par with the original     
OL,6,BiMac and Technics 1210.                
OL,7,FI'm not the only one to think so - the 
OL,8,Fproduction designer on the original    
OL,9,FMamma Mia film also liked its looks -  
OL,10,Fas there are three Micron handhelds    
OL,11,Fused in the end credits sequence.      
OL,12,EI'd posted a picture on a Facebook     
OL,13,Eforum for TV studio enthusiasts and it 
OL,14,Egenerated a number of comments and     
OL,15,Efond memories. Micron was thought to be
OL,16,Erobust and reliable and was the        
OL,17,Emainstay of UK TV radiomic kit until   
OL,18,Ethe early 2000's.                      
OL,19,ASince making the video a statue was    
OL,20,Aunveiled in Bury, Lancashire, of the   
OL,21,Alate comedienne Victoria Wood, cast in 
OL,22,Abronze, complete with a Micron TX      
OL,23,Aseries handheld.                       
OL,24,ASinclair C5BSpectrum 48KCNewsFMainIndex
